  "time_ut": 1660618549,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b85\u0ba9\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd: \u0b95\u0bb0\u0bc1 \u0b9c\u0baf\u0b9a\u0bc2\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Everyone should come forward to save the country: Karu Jayasuriya",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former Speaker and President of National Movement for Social Justice Karu Jayasuriya has said that Sri Lanka is going through an unprecedented period in its history, and all citizens should come forward to save the country.",
        "He said this during a meeting with union leaders. He further said,",
        "We feel that you, representing the unions, have a more important duty than anyone else. You represent millions of working people in the country.",
        "Your constituents direct all activities that support the country's administration, production and day-to-day living activities. We invite union leaders to participate in this discussion because we understand your value and strength.",
        "Rulers should consider it their prime duty to bring people's lives back to normalcy. Uninterrupted electricity supply for 24 hours, fair pricing of food items including palma, gas etc. should be done quickly. Then the industrial sector, export and tourism sector will grow rapidly.",
        "The impact on educational activities during the last two years should also be immediately rectified. Education should be considered as our most valuable investment.",
        "The agricultural sector, which has suffered complete destruction, should be rebuilt. He says the previous government had taken wrong decisions depending on the agriculture sector. (a)"
      ],
